OL,3,COver 900 classroom assistants working
OL,4,Cwithout access check
OL,6,FConcerns have been raised about the
OL,7,Fnumber of classroom assistants in
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland who have been working
OL,9,Fwithout the appropriate background
OL,10,Fchecks.
OL,12,FAccess NI checks are a legal
OL,13,Frequirement for people who work with
OL,14,Fchildren and other vulnerable
OL,15,Findividuals to protect them from harm.
OL,17,FEducation Minister Pau Givan revealed
OL,18,Fthat as of 29 January, 909 classroom
OL,19,Fassistants were working in Northern
OL,20,FIreland without receiving the outcome
OL,21,Fof these checks.
