OL,3,COver 900 classroom assistants working
OL,4,Cwithout access check
OL,6,F"This includes staff awaiting the
OL,7,Foutcome of the check to be 'supervised
OL,8,Fat all times by someone vetted to
OL,9,Fwork."
OL,11,FThe Education Authority or (EA) is the
OL,12,Femploying authority for the majority
OL,13,Fof classroom assistants in Northern
OL,14,FIreland.
OL,16,FMr Givan said the EA has processes in
OL,17,Fplace to follow-up and confirm that
OL,18,Fchecks that were not able to be
OL,19,Fcompleted prior to engagement have
OL,20,Fbeen completed.
